{
    "poem_title": "LE DIMANCHE MATIN",
    "author": "Henri Murger",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1861",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Le samedi dit au dimanche :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "\" Tout le village est endormi ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "L'aiguille vers minuit se penche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "C'est maintenant ton tour, ami.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Moi, je suis las de ma journée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Je veux aller dormir aussi ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Viens vite, ton heure est sonnée. \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Le dimanche dit : \" me voici ! \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le samedi dit au dimanche :\n\" Tout le village est endormi ;\nL'aiguille vers minuit se penche,\nC'est maintenant ton tour, ami.\nMoi, je suis las de ma journée,\nJe veux aller dormir aussi ;\nViens vite, ton heure est sonnée. \"\nLe dimanche dit : \" me voici ! \""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Il s'éveille en bâillant derrière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "La nuit aux étincelles d'or,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Et frotte des mains sa paupière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Et s'habille en bâillant encor.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Puis, quand il a fait sa toilette,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Pour aller lui donner l'éveil,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Il frappe à l'huis de la chambrette",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Où dort son ami le soleil.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il s'éveille en bâillant derrière\nLa nuit aux étincelles d'or,\nEt frotte des mains sa paupière,\nEt s'habille en bâillant encor.\nPuis, quand il a fait sa toilette,\nPour aller lui donner l'éveil,\nIl frappe à l'huis de la chambrette\nOù dort son ami le soleil."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "\" De votre alcôve orientale",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Sortez, dit-il, grand paresseux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Stella, votre sœur matinale,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "À l'horizon ferme les yeux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Pour vous saluer, l'alouette",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Chante déjà sur les sillons ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Venez, venez, c'est jour de fête,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Choisissez vos plus beaux rayons ! \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" De votre alcôve orientale\nSortez, dit-il, grand paresseux ;\nStella, votre sœur matinale,\nÀ l'horizon ferme les yeux.\nPour vous saluer, l'alouette\nChante déjà sur les sillons ;\nVenez, venez, c'est jour de fête,\nChoisissez vos plus beaux rayons ! \""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Le dimanche sur la montagne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Monte, et regarde autour de lui :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "\" Ils dorment tous dans la campagne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Dit-il, ne faisons pas de bruit. \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Et doucement vers le village",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Il redescend à petits pas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Et dit au coq : \" par ton ramage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Mon ami, ne me trahis pas. \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le dimanche sur la montagne\nMonte, et regarde autour de lui :\n\" Ils dorment tous dans la campagne,\nDit-il, ne faisons pas de bruit. \"\nEt doucement vers le village\nIl redescend à petits pas\nEt dit au coq : \" par ton ramage,\nMon ami, ne me trahis pas. \""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Après la bonne nuit passée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Pour vous accueillir au réveil",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "On voit sourire, à la croisée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Le dimanche assis au soleil.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Et si quelque enfant paresseuse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Rêve un peu tard sur l'oreiller,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Il lui laisse finir, heureuse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Son rêve avant de l'éveiller.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Après la bonne nuit passée,\nPour vous accueillir au réveil\nOn voit sourire, à la croisée,\nLe dimanche assis au soleil.\nEt si quelque enfant paresseuse\nRêve un peu tard sur l'oreiller,\nIl lui laisse finir, heureuse,\nSon rêve avant de l'éveiller."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "C'est lui, le voilà, le dimanche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Avec le mois de mai nouveau ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "L'amandier met sa robe blanche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Le bleu de ciel azure l'eau.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Les fleurs du jardin sont écloses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "On croirait voir le paradis ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "La violette parle aux roses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Le chêne orgueilleux parle au buis.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est lui, le voilà, le dimanche,\nAvec le mois de mai nouveau ;\nL'amandier met sa robe blanche,\nLe bleu de ciel azure l'eau.\nLes fleurs du jardin sont écloses,\nOn croirait voir le paradis ;\nLa violette parle aux roses,\nLe chêne orgueilleux parle au buis."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Au bord du nid, battant des ailes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "L'oiseau chante en se réveillant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Et dit bonjour aux hirondelles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Qui reviennent de l'Orient.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Dans son bel habit du dimanche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Le chardonneret marche fier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Et vole aussi de branche en branche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Et jette sa chanson dans l'air.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au bord du nid, battant des ailes,\nL'oiseau chante en se réveillant,\nEt dit bonjour aux hirondelles\nQui reviennent de l'Orient.\nDans son bel habit du dimanche\nLe chardonneret marche fier,\nEt vole aussi de branche en branche,\nEt jette sa chanson dans l'air."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Il apporte dans les familles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "À chacun ses petits cadeaux :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Des rubans pour les jeunes filles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Et pour les enfants, des gâteaux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Il ne fait que chanter et rire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Il débouche les vieux flacons,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Et, le soir, de sa poche il tire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Les flûtes et les violons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il apporte dans les familles\nÀ chacun ses petits cadeaux :\nDes rubans pour les jeunes filles,\nEt pour les enfants, des gâteaux.\nIl ne fait que chanter et rire,\nIl débouche les vieux flacons,\nEt, le soir, de sa poche il tire\nLes flûtes et les violons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Voyez combien l'on est tranquille",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Dans tout le village aujourd'hui ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Le moulin à la roue agile",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Et l'enclume ont cessé leur bruit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Les bœufs ruminent à la crèche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Libres du joug et du brancard,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Et la charrue avec la bêche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Se reposent sous le hangar.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Voyez combien l'on est tranquille\nDans tout le village aujourd'hui ;\nLe moulin à la roue agile\nEt l'enclume ont cessé leur bruit.\nLes bœufs ruminent à la crèche,\nLibres du joug et du brancard,\nEt la charrue avec la bêche\nSe reposent sous le hangar."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Tout le monde paraît à l'aise,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "On s'aborde d'un air content.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "\" Comment va ton père, Thérèse ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "— Vilhem, comment va votre enfant ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "— Bon temps, voisin, pour la futaille !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "— Voisin, bon temps pour le grenier ! \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Personne aujourd'hui ne travaille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Excepté le ménétrier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tout le monde paraît à l'aise,\nOn s'aborde d'un air content.\n\" Comment va ton père, Thérèse ?\n— Vilhem, comment va votre enfant ?\n— Bon temps, voisin, pour la futaille !\n— Voisin, bon temps pour le grenier ! \"\nPersonne aujourd'hui ne travaille,\nExcepté le ménétrier."
        }
    ],
